Weathering the B2B E-Storm

Implementing a B2B marketing strategy can be difficult. The
market is lucrative, but successful approaches are not as
obvious as they are in consumer markets. Adam discusses an
Accenture report that clears things up a bit.

http://clickz.com/article/cz.3999.html





